    "inspiration": "ARK Business (https://www.ark.business/)",
    "replaceability": "This frontend is a functional placeholder. All visual components are built to be ripped and replaced with Figma-exported assets and production designs. Prioritize clean separation of logic and presentation so the visual layer can be swapped without rewriting business logic, state management, or data fetching."
